post.description:
Put associates a group with a namespace.

/namespace/<namespaceid>/groups/<groupid>
    {
        has_read = 1,
        has_delete = 0,
        has_create = 0,
        has_update = 0,
        has_namespace = 0,
    }

Transparently creates a permission object.

put.description: Modify groups that can access a namespace.

patch.description: Patch the permissions of an existing group for a namespace.

delete.description:
Delete disassociates a group with a namespace.

Transparently deletes the permission object.
